        <div class="anat-legend">
          <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">1</span><div><strong>Status Dot</strong><span>Small colored circle (border-radius: 9999px). Color changes based on status semantic.</span></div></div>
          <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">2</span><div><strong>Icon</strong><span>Optional icon element. Hidden by default. Toggled via Show Icon boolean.</span></div></div>
          <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">3</span><div><strong>Label</strong><span>Optional text label. Visible by default. Defaults to "Status". Toggled via Show Label boolean.</span></div></div>
          <div class="anat-legend-item"><span class="anat-marker-inline">4</span><div><strong>Container</strong><span>Horizontal auto-layout, 4px padding, 4px gap, transparent bg, 6px radius.</span></div></div>
